casebody.data:
Tuesday, October 3, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

95-1803. State ex rel. The Cincinnati Post v. Cincinnati.

In Mandamus.

On answer of respondent, motion for judgment on the pleadings, and motion to strike motion for judgment on the pleadings.

Sua sponte, alternative writ granted.

Douglas and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., would also grant the motion to strike.
